Enhanced Datagrid Control using jQuery 1.6.4
 - by      : Robert J. Secord, B.Sc.
 - version : 0.1
 - web     : http://lab.robsecord.com/jquery/datagrid/
 - github  : https://github.com/robsecord/jQuery-Datagrid

Features:
 - Ajax or JSON Data Source
 - 3 Data Source Types: Number, String, Date
 - Full Customization via CSS Themes
 - i18n Support
 - Column Sorting (Client-Side)
 - Column Freezing
 - Column Reordering
 - Column Resizing
 - Configurable Column Model
 - Configurable Date Formatting
 - Alternating Rows/Columns
 - Hover Rows/Columns/Cells
 - Spacer Column/Row

Features to come:
 - 4th Data Source Type: Currency
 - Column Sorting (Server-Side)
 - Lazy Loading (North & South)
 - Column Hiding/Revealing
 - Column Model Persistence via Cookies